# QA & testing

## Test pyramid

1. **Unit** (`composeApp/src/commonTest`) — fast, deterministic; fake repositories/services.
2. **Instrumented** (`androidApp/src/androidInstrumentedTest`) — Compose UI smoke on critical paths.
3. **Manual** (`firebase-appdistribution-testcases.yaml`) — Firebase App Distribution testers (currently **v76**).

## Unit tests

- Pure domain: no mocks (`NutritionAiPlanner`, `WeekCalendar`, `GroceryListPresentation`, codecs).
- Screen models: `runTest` + `TestDispatcher`; `advanceUntilIdle()` after `scope.launch` updates.
- Fakes must implement **full** interfaces — update when APIs grow (`FakeAuthRepository`, instrumented fakes).
- **i18n parity:** `*LocaleStringsTest` (Auth, Home, Nutrition, Household, Sharing) — every key in all 8 locales.
- **Navigation:** `AppNavigatorTest`, `AppNavigationTest`, `HouseholdNavigationContractTest`.
- **Theme:** `AppIconsTest` — no broken semantic aliases.
- **Invite/collab:** parsers, OTP, preview RPC; Deno tests for edge pure helpers.

```bash
./gradlew :composeApp:testDebugUnitTest
```

## Instrumented tests

- `createAndroidComposeRule` + `AppTheme` + `InstrumentedKoinHost` / `InstrumentedNutritionFakes`.
- `onNodeWithTag` over text; `performScrollTo` before off-screen nodes.
- `InstrumentedComposeTest.waitFor` / `waitUntil` — no `Thread.sleep`.
- Scope: integration smoke (navigation, grocery add, meal-plan AI button, hub cards, touch targets).
- Deep CRUD rules belong in `NutritionScreenModelTest` / domain unit tests.

```bash
./gradlew :androidApp:assembleDebugAndroidTest
```

CI runs instrumented on PR and `main` push; local optional via emulator.

## Manual QA (Firebase)

Update `firebase-appdistribution-testcases.yaml` when user-visible flows change:

- Bump top-level `version` and `updated` date.
- Add `id`, `title`, `steps`, `expected` per scenario.
- Distinguish editable grocery vs AI read-only (terracotta) suggestions.
- Wave C cases: `wavec-dark-theme-napolitan`, `wavec-wide-grocery-side-panel`, `wavec-wide-meal-plan-columns`, `wavec-ai-grocery-terracotta-accent`.
- Hub: grocery + meal plan entry; back returns to hub.
- Crashlytics: `crashlytics-smoke` on builds with `google-services.json`.
- Household: `household-member-avatar` — member row photos, self + dependant upload (requires `member-avatars` bucket + migration `20250703000000`).

Release workflow embeds checklist excerpt in Firebase release notes.

## Before merge

```bash
./gradlew :composeApp:testDebugUnitTest
./gradlew :composeApp:compileDebugAndroidTestKotlinAndroid
```

When touching invites/migrations:

```bash
./scripts/test-supabase-invite-edge.sh
./scripts/verify-supabase-household.sh   # staging, needs credentials
```

## Test naming

- Unit: `*Test.kt` under mirrored package path.
- Instrumented: `*InstrumentedTest.kt` in `androidInstrumentedTest/.../ui/`.
- Fakes: `Fake*` / `Instrumented*Fakes.kt`.
